    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "TIMETABLE EFFECTIVE AUGUST 1st, 1950\nВСРА\nDC-6 Sleeper Service\nCANADA-USA-HAWAII-FIJI\nAUSTRALIA-NEW ZEALAND\nBritish Commonwealth\nPacific Airlines Ltd.\nI previous lists cancelled",
      "You sleep like a top in these roomy, luxuriously appointed, full-length\nsleepers.\nArrive at your\ndestination after a good night's sleep,\nrefreshed-ready for business or pleasure.\nAsk your Travel Agent about the B.C.P.A. Service\nB.C.P.A. Agents\nAUSTRALIA: T.A.A.. 339 Swanston St.. Melbourne. Cl. Booking\nOffices all States.\nNEW ZEALAND\nand FIll:\nN.Z.N.A.C.,\nMercantile\nChambers,\nCustoms St., East Auckland.\nAgencies throughout N.Z.\nHONOLULU: Theo. H. Davies \u0026 Co., Limited, Davies Building,\nU.S.A.: B.C.P.A. Booking\nOffice, 347\nStockton St.,\nSan Francisco.\nPhone YUkon 6-6971.\nB.O.A.C.\nNew York 17. N.Y. Also CHICAGO, LOS ANGELES, WASHING-\nTON.\nCANADA: T.C.A., Hotel Vancouver, B.C. Offices major cities.\nU.K. and elsewhere: B.O.A.C.\nB.C.P.A. HEAD OFFICE :\nA.P.A. Building, 53 Martin Place, Sydney. Phone BW 2741 (15 lines).\nSAN FRANCISCO:\n347 Stockton St., San Francisco.\nPhone YUkon 6-6971.\nPRINTED IN AUSTRALIA.\nJohn Sands Pty. Ltd., Sydney\n5091/8\n2014.094."
    ],
